      <li>definition of an element of representation that has a value that is a real number;</li>
      <li>definition of an element of representation that has a value that is a sequence of representation elements;</li>
      <li>definition of an element of representation that has a value that is a set of representation elements;</li>
      <li>items within the scope of application module <module_ref linkend="extended_date:1_scope">Extended date</module_ref>, ISO/TS 10303-1776;</li>
      <li>items within the scope of application module <module_ref linkend="foundation_representation:1_scope">Foundation representation</module_ref>, ISO/TS 10303-1006.</li>
